thread.title: BRIEF-Denizbank FY 2017 Net Profit Rises To 1.88 Bln Lira

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Denizbank FY 2017 Net Profit Rises To 1.88 Bln Lira
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - DENIZBANK:
* REPORTED WEDNESDAY FY 2017 NET PROFIT OF 1.88 BLN LIRA VERSUS 1.41 BLN LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 NET INTEREST INCOME OF 4.86 LIRA VERSUS 4.02 BLN LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 NET FEE AND COMMISSION INCOME 1.51 BLN LIRA VERSUS 1.19 BLN LIRA YEAR AGO
* NON-PERFORMING LOANS AT END OF 2017 3.63 BLN LIRA VERSUS 3.29 BLN LIRA YEAR AGO
